# ts-for-gir Cursor Rules

The Cursor rules for this project have been organized into multiple focused files.
Please see the `.cursor/rules/` directory for specific rules:

- `ts-for-gir-workspace.mdc` - Workspace structure and package organization
- `type-generation.mdc` - Type generation process, templates, and generators
- `cli-usage.mdc` - CLI usage and generation commands
- `development-workflow.mdc` - Development workflow and contribution
- `gir-sources.mdc` - GIR file sources and paths
- `gjs-examples.mdc` - GJS examples and patterns
- `typescript-best-practices.mdc` - TypeScript coding standards

Each rule file is focused on a specific aspect of the project to help AI assistants
understand and work with the codebase more effectively.
